sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as trainer-controller-manager<br/>Go Operator
    participant TrainingPod as Training Pod (node-0)<br/>29500/TCP, 28080/TCP
    participant WorkerPods as Training Worker Pods<br/>29500/TCP
    participant CacheHead as data-cache (head)<br/>Arrow Flight gRPC
    participant CacheWorker as data-cache (worker)<br/>Arrow Flight gRPC

    Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: TrainJob Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-trainer-kubeflow-org-v1alpha1-trainjob<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS, TLS auto-rotated<br/>Auth: API Server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: AdmissionReview response
    K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch TrainJob + read referenced runtime<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Server-side apply: JobSet, PodGroup,<br/>NetworkPolicy, SSH Secret/ConfigMap<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over Controller,WorkerPods: Flow 2: Distributed Training (PyTorch)

    K8sAPI-->>TrainingPod: Pods scheduled via JobSet
    K8sAPI-->>WorkerPods: Worker pods scheduled

    WorkerPods->>TrainingPod: torchrun rendezvous<br/>29500/TCP, No encryption
    TrainingPod->>WorkerPods: NCCL all-reduce<br/>Dynamic/TCP, No encryption<br/>(gradient synchronization)

    Note over Controller,TrainingPod: Flow 3: RHAI Progression Tracking

    Controller->>K8sAPI: List pods (find primary pod IP)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>TrainingPod: GET http://podIP:28080/metrics<br/>28080/TCP HTTP, No encryption<br/>Auth: None (NetworkPolicy enforced)
    TrainingPod-->>Controller: JSON metrics (progress %, epoch, ETA)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Patch TrainJob annotations<br/>with trainer status JSON<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over CacheHead,CacheWorker: Flow 4: Data Cache (Optional)

    CacheHead->>CacheHead: Read Iceberg metadata<br/>(METADATA_LOC)
    CacheHead->>CacheWorker: do_put: assign data files<br/>Arrow Flight gRPC
    CacheWorker->>CacheWorker: Load data into<br/>in-memory Arrow tables
    TrainingPod->>CacheHead: Query partition endpoints<br/>Arrow Flight gRPC
    CacheHead-->>TrainingPod: Worker endpoint list
    TrainingPod->>CacheWorker: do_get: fetch data rows<br/>Arrow Flight gRPC
    CacheWorker-->>TrainingPod: Arrow RecordBatch data
